wt.change2.handler

Class DefaultChangeItemOriginationHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • wt.change2.handler.DefaultChangeItemOriginationHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChangeItemOriginationHandler

    public class DefaultChangeItemOriginationHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements ChangeItemOriginationHandler
    Default handler for validating if the originatedBy and originatingLocation is a valid for the change item. This handler is registered in service.properties under the name "wt.change2.handler.ChangeItemOriginationHandler" and requestor "wt.change2.VersionableChangeItem".

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: true
